scene.message:
Maki: The town's pretty{nl}
different from your town too,{nl}
isn't it!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: It's a weird feeling.{nl}
The faces are familiar, but{nl}
something's off about them.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Just inside the school{nl}
is way too cramped a stage{nl}
for me!{waitkey}Wahahahaha!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: I've no business with{nl}
the school. I just want to{nl}
beat him and be done with it.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: True, you're right. We{nl}
played the Persona Game, went{nl}
to visit, and then that{nl}
incident happened...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: The Persona Game?{wait_fr:32}{nl}
...A visit? To whom? What{nl}
are you talking about?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:32}You don't{nl}
remember?{waitkey}{clearbox}Or are you not the Mayuzumi{nl}
we know?{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:32}Either way, it seems{nl}
best we withdraw for now.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, {ctl0f:1}, Naito said{nl}
to come to the library,{nl}
right?{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's at least hear him out{nl}
before we head outside.{waitkey}{ret}
